name: 即席BATH_SOMA
description: by Rebecca Merlic - Her nine NFTs on display are fractions from "TheCityAsAHouse". Traditional notions on private spaces are thus subjected to a reassessment in the 30 to a maximum of 75 second clips and liquefies into countless encounters from the public - now privatized - space. At the center of all these narratives is always the question of what it means to feel at home and what conditions are needed to do so.
